ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (IRAN) REGULATIONS in order to contribute to international efforts by like-minded countries to recognize the steps taken under the Joint Comprehensive Plan of Action, while continuing to pressure its government to make additional reforms and restrict its access to sensitive goods.
